item.title: Portal codes/how do you make them tele you somewhere?
item.dc:creator: @watch_n_lern watch n lern
item.description:
@watch_n_lern wrote:

heres an example from my server:

makeGlobalObject(2404, 3102, 2473, 0, 10); // Skill portal 1

if (objectID == 2473 && objectX == 2404 && objectY == 3102) { triggerTele(2038, 4487, 0); }
you need to specify where the portal is, and where it teles you to.
